**StreamOrbitChart**  
**Description:**  
Renders real-time numeric data in a smooth, orbit-style scrolling visual layout for live dashboards.

```markdown
# StreamOrbitChart - Live Stream Visualizer

StreamOrbitChart transforms incoming metric values into a circular, orbiting chart with smooth transitions.

## Features
- Unique orbit-style layout  
- Realtime metric scroll  
- Matplotlib-powered

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamOrbitChart.git
cd StreamOrbitChart
python visualize.py
